{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e598fc3038","title":"在西藏军区关于印军入侵雅斜儿情况报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fbf0ae75e1","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"e598fc3038"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"a1980879a0","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军西藏军区1959年9月1日24时关于对雅斜儿印军侦察情况给总参谋部、外交部的报告。"},{"id":"a3b8a5c707","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。陈，指陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。"},{"id":"e589148da3","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"年8月25日，一支印度武装部队侵入属于我国领土的朗久地区，袭击我马及墩（即毛泽东批语中的“米基顿”）边防哨所，挑起武装冲突。我边防部队为了自卫，被道予以还击。"},{"id":"b6f7cd9e6b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"雅斜儿，位于东经93°12，北纬23°38，是在中国境内，而且在“麦克马洪线”以北。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c2ba6f48be","type":"title","text":"在西藏军区关于印军人侵雅斜儿情况报告\"上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038"},{"id":"a1980879a0","type":"paragraph","text":"周、陈响同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038"},{"id":"a3b8a5c707","type":"paragraph","text":"雅斜儿的印军跑了，廿六日跑的，是在廿五日migiiadm（米基顿）即朗久区一打的影响之下跑掉的。请与总参谋部联系，侵地未跑的还有几处，告我为盼！又，雅斜儿在什么地方，亦请查告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038"},{"id":"e589148da3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038"},{"id":"b6f7cd9e6b","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038"}],"page":{"id":"a6d27942d5","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e598fc3038","start":341,"end":341}}}},"__N_SSG":true}